title: Staats Card Creator

creator: Jordan Grant
descriptionHtml:
Staats makes designing your own trading cards simple and fun! 🙌 Create quality cards with hundreds of templates and thousands of high quality graphics.

A card creator for every sport: soccer, basketball, baseball, cricket, football, hockey, tennis, golf, MMA, music, poke, yugioh, — Staats is the ultimate card maker app.

Design your card in 30 seconds and have it ready to post on any social network: Facebook, Pinterest and Twitter. Make cards for your friends and family, or your favorite athletes!

Stay on brand with our Team Kit feature - upload your images and have them available to use anytime, anywhere.

How to Use Staats
1. Quick Create
Choose a photo, choose a sport, and bam! We generate your card! Polish it up with a few extra details and you're good to go.

2. Curated Templates
Pick from our gallery of sports stars, then modify the template to suit your needs. Use Google Image Search to get 4K quality images, wallpapers, and custom graphics to use on your cards!

3. Make once, get all designs
Add your card information once, and view your card in every style - no fiddling around with text boxes and alignment - we will generate a polished card, every time.

4. Edit pictures like a pro
Use our image editor to crop and resize your images to fit the card perfectly.

5. Show it off to the world
Share designs directly to Instagram, WhatsApp, email, or simply save to your device.

Staats Cards Are Digital Trading Cards
• Recreate trading card designs
• Capture sports memories with an animated GIF trading card
• Exchange cards with your friends
• Upload your best designs to Trophy Case and get a shareable link

Create Designs Quickly
Use Search to find templates faster. Tap the search bar to immediately see a list of all the templates available on the app.

Staats = Quality
Use Staats to make trading cards for any sport. A one stop shop to make your awesome designs come to life!

---
Follow @staatsapp on Instagram for tips. Got feedback? Email mystaats[at]gmail.com
---
Staats claims no affiliation to official organizations or sports leagues, including but not limited to: NBA, NHL, MLB, NFL, FIFA, UFC, IPL, Pokémon, Yugioh
Images displayed in the app are for demonstrative purposes only.
descriptionShort: Fast and simple! Make customized, social media ready trading cards for any sport

A card creator for every sport: basketball, baseball, cricket, football, hockey, tennis, golf, MMA, music, poke, yugioh, — NinjaFT is the ultimate card maker app.

Design your card in 30 seconds and have it ready to post on any social network: Facebook, Pinterest and Twitter. Make cards for your friends and family, or your favorite athletes!

Stay on brand with our Team Kit feature - upload your images and have them available to use anytime, anywhere.

How to Use NinjaFT
1. Quick Create
Choose a photo, choose a sport, and bam! We generate your card! Polish it up with a few extra details and you're good to go.

2. Curated Templates
Pick from our gallery of sports stars, then modify the template to suit your needs. Use Google Image Search to get 4K quality images, wallpapers, and custom graphics to use on your cards!

3. Make once, get all designs
Add your card information once, and view your card in every style - no fiddling around with text boxes and alignment - we will generate a polished card, every time.

4. Edit pictures like a pro
Use our image editor to crop and resize your images to fit the card perfectly.

5. Show it off to the world
Share designs directly to Instagram, WhatsApp, email, or simply save to your device.

NinjaFT Cards Are Digital Trading Cards
• Recreate trading card designs
• Capture sports memories with an animated GIF trading card
• Exchange cards with your friends
• Upload your best designs to Trophy Case and get a shareable link

Create Designs Quickly
Use Search to find templates faster. Tap the search bar to immediately see a list of all the templates available on the app.

NinjaFT = Quality
Use NinjaFT to make trading cards for any sport. A one stop shop to make your awesome designs come to life!

Mint and buy NFT collectibles with NinjaFT! Upload your artwork and have it minted in seconds. Then, transfer your new NFT to your crypto wallet.

Start your collection with NFT packs, and receive three randomly selected items. Purchase a rare pack for exclusive NFTs, playable in the upcoming NinjaVerse.

Check in every day for free NFT giveaways! Check the Airdrops feature for these exclusive items.

NinjaFT makes designing your own trading cards simple and fun! 🙌 Create quality cards with hundreds of templates and thousands of high quality graphics.

A card creator for every sport: basketball, baseball, cricket, football, hockey, tennis, golf, MMA, music, poke, yugioh, — NinjaFT is the ultimate card maker app.

Design your card in 30 seconds and have it ready to post on any social network: Facebook, Pinterest and Twitter. Make cards for your friends and family, or your favorite athletes!

Stay on brand with our Team Kit feature - upload your images and have them available to use anytime, anywhere.

How to Use NinjaFT
1. Quick Create
Choose a photo, choose a sport, and bam! We generate your card! Polish it up with a few extra details and you're good to go.

2. Curated Templates
Pick from our gallery of sports stars, then modify the template to suit your needs. Use Google Image Search to get 4K quality images, wallpapers, and custom graphics to use on your cards!

3. Make once, get all designs
Add your card information once, and view your card in every style - no fiddling around with text boxes and alignment - we will generate a polished card, every time.

4. Edit pictures like a pro
Use our image editor to crop and resize your images to fit the card perfectly.

5. Show it off to the world
Share designs directly to Instagram, WhatsApp, email, or simply save to your device.

NinjaFT Cards Are Digital Trading Cards
• Recreate trading card designs
• Capture sports memories with an animated GIF trading card
• Exchange cards with your friends
• Upload your best designs to Trophy Case and get a shareable link

Create Designs Quickly
Use Search to find templates faster. Tap the search bar to immediately see a list of all the templates available on the app.

NinjaFT = Quality
Use NinjaFT to make trading cards for any sport. A one stop shop to make your awesome designs come to life!

Mint and buy NFT collectibles with NinjaFT! Upload your artwork and have it minted in seconds. Then, transfer your new NFT to your crypto wallet.

Start your collection with NFT packs, and receive three randomly selected items. Purchase a rare pack for exclusive NFTs, playable in the upcoming NinjaVerse.

Check in every day for free NFT giveaways! Check the Airdrops feature for these exclusive items.

NinjaFT makes designing your own trading cards simple and fun! 🙌 Create quality cards with hundreds of templates and thousands of high quality graphics.

A card creator for every sport: basketball, baseball, cricket, football, hockey, tennis, golf, MMA, music, poke, yugioh, — NinjaFT is the ultimate card maker app.

Design your card in 30 seconds and have it ready to post on any social network: Facebook, Pinterest and Twitter. Make cards for your friends and family, or your favorite athletes!

Stay on brand with our Team Kit feature - upload your images and have them available to use anytime, anywhere.

How to Use NinjaFT
1. Quick Create
Choose a photo, choose a sport, and bam! We generate your card! Polish it up with a few extra details and you're good to go.

2. Curated Templates
Pick from our gallery of sports stars, then modify the template to suit your needs. Use Google Image Search to get 4K quality images, wallpapers, and custom graphics to use on your cards!

3. Make once, get all designs
Add your card information once, and view your card in every style - no fiddling around with text boxes and alignment - we will generate a polished card, every time.

4. Edit pictures like a pro
Use our image editor to crop and resize your images to fit the card perfectly.

5. Show it off to the world
Share designs directly to Instagram, WhatsApp, email, or simply save to your device.

NinjaFT Cards Are Digital Trading Cards
• Recreate trading card designs
• Capture sports memories with an animated GIF trading card
• Exchange cards with your friends
• Upload your best designs to Trophy Case and get a shareable link

Create Designs Quickly
Use Search to find templates faster. Tap the search bar to immediately see a list of all the templates available on the app.

NinjaFT = Quality
Use NinjaFT to make trading cards for any sport. A one stop shop to make your awesome designs come to life!

title: NFT Game - NinjaFT

creator: Staats Customs Inc.
descriptionHtml:
NinjaFT is for NFT beginners. Join a welcoming community, fun NFT metaverse, and engage in NFT Ninja Battles with characters and items you own - which you can buy, sell and trade.

Start your collection with NFT packs, and receive three NFTs. Purchase a rare pack for exclusive NFTs, playable in the NinjaVerse. Ninja Battles are live!

Purchase awesome NFT Art and join a group of likeminded collectors and traders.

Mint and buy NFT collectibles with NinjaFT! Upload your artwork and have it minted in seconds. Then, transfer your new NFT to your crypto wallet.

Check in every day for free NFT giveaways! Check the Airdrops feature for these exclusive items.

NinjaFT makes designing your own NFT trading cards simple and fun! Create quality cards with hundreds of templates and thousands of high quality graphics.

descriptionHtml:
NinjaFT is for NFT beginners. Join a welcoming community, fun NFT metaverse, and engage in NFT Ninja Battles with characters and items you own - which you can buy, sell and trade.

Start your collection with NFT packs, and receive three NFTs. Purchase a rare pack for exclusive NFTs, playable in the NinjaVerse. Ninja Battles are live!

Purchase awesome NFT Art and join a group of likeminded collectors and traders.

Mint and buy NFT collectibles with NinjaFT! Upload your artwork and have it minted in seconds. Then, transfer your new NFT to your crypto wallet.

Check in every day for free NFT giveaways! Check the Airdrops feature for these exclusive items.

NinjaFT makes designing your own NFT trading cards simple and fun! Create quality cards with hundreds of templates and thousands of high quality graphics.

---

NinjaFT is for NFT beginners. Join a welcoming community, fun NFT metaverse, and engage in NFT Ninja Battles with characters and items you own - which you can buy, sell and trade.

Start your collection with NFT packs, and receive three NFTs. Purchase a rare pack for exclusive NFTs, playable in the NinjaVerse. Ninja Battles are live!

Purchase awesome NFT Art and join a group of likeminded collectors and traders.

Mint and buy NFT collectibles with NinjaFT! Upload your artwork and have it minted in seconds. Then, transfer your new NFT to your crypto wallet.

Check in every day for free NFT giveaways! Check the Airdrops feature for these exclusive items.

NinjaFT makes designing your own NFT trading cards simple and fun! Create quality cards with hundreds of templates and thousands of high quality graphics.

title: NFT Game - NinjaFT

creator: Staats Customs Inc.
descriptionHtml:
Play online with ninjas around the world in a 1v1 showdown. Unleash a flurry of weapon attacks, pet attacks and special skills to overwhelm your opponent.

Join over 80,000 active players, and climb the leaderboard to win amazing prizes!

Gameplay
Fight online using basic turn based gameplay, with strategy baked into every aspect - elemental damage, rage, and spells.

Spells
Unleash powerful spells to gain an advantage over your foe. You can block attacks, save your ninja from imminent death, prevent healing potions, or double down on damage for a turn. Check out the Store and Redeem Shop for spells and use them in battle by clicking Swap.

Fusion
Combine multiple NFTs to unleash a more powerful NFT! You can combine 5, 7, or 10 NFTs to Fusion Swap. These powerful NFTs take up your swap for the turn, so use them wisely to counter your foe.

NFT Ready
You can construct your ninja with NFTs you own to build the strongest ninja! Collect the rarest, most powerful items in the game.

Crypto Enabled
Earn coins for playing, and redeem those in-game coins for cryptocurrency. See "Cash Out" for this feature and earn BNB today!

Collectibles
Purchase NFTs from our Candy Machine collections such as Jungle Club and SAM THE SAMURAI. The collections feature their own private communities, exclusive in-game power-ups, and increase your earning potential in NinjaFT.

Simulation Mode
Earn coins passively with your NFTs! Your entire collection can be verified to earn coins daily in Simulation Mode.

Daily Airdrops
Check in every day for free NFT giveaways! Check the Airdrops feature for these exclusive items.

NinjaFT is one of the first P2E blockchain games on the App Store! Join a strong gaming community that loves to battle and trade!

---
Got feedback? Email staatsapp[at]gmail.com
Privacy Policy: www.staatsapp.com/privacy
Terms of Use: www.staatsapp.com/terms
descriptionShort: Online PvP NFT Game - Play to Earn Crypto

Play online with ninjas around the world in a 1v1 showdown. Unleash a flurry of weapon attacks, pet attacks and special skills to overwhelm your opponent.

Join over 100,000 players, and climb the leaderboard to win amazing prizes!

Gameplay
Fight online using basic turn based gameplay, with strategy baked into every aspect - elemental damage, rage, and spells.

Spells
Unleash powerful spells to gain an advantage over your foe. You can block attacks, save your ninja from imminent death, prevent healing potions, or double down on damage for a turn. Check out the Store and Redeem Shop for spells and use them in battle by clicking Swap.

Fusion
Combine multiple items to unleash a more powerful item! You can combine 5, 7, or 10 items to Fusion Swap. Use them wisely to counter your foe.

NFT Ready
You can construct your ninja with NFTs you own to build the strongest ninja! Collect the rarest, most powerful items in the game.

Collectibles
Purchase items from our Candy Machine collections such as Jungle Club and SAM THE SAMURAI. The collections feature their own private communities, exclusive in-game power-ups, and increase your earning potential in NinjaFT.

Simulation Mode
Earn coins passively with your NFTs! Your entire collection can be verified to earn coins daily in Simulation Mode.

Daily Airdrops
Check in every day for free giveaways! Check the Airdrops feature for these exclusive items.

NinjaFT is one of the first blockchain games on the App Store! Join a strong gaming community that loves to battle and trade!

---
